"title": "5698: guardian",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "5698",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<h2>Human guardianship</h2>\n<h3>Responsibility for people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal4:2\">GAL 4:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ruth3:9-Ruth3:13\">RUT 3:9–3:13</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs10:1\">2KI 10:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor4:14-1Cor4:15\">1CO 4:14–4:15</a></p>\n<h3>Responsibility for other things</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:28\">GEN 1:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:5\">GEN 9:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen9:12\">GEN 9:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Lev25:23\">LEV 25:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps8:6-Ps8:8\">PSA 8:6–8:8</a></p>\n<h2>God's guardianship of people</h2>\n<h3>He loves and cares</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer31:3\">JER 31:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps103:13-Ps103:14\">PSA 103:13–103:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:14\">PSA 139:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:32\">MAT 6:32</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke12:7\">LUK 12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph2:4-Eph2:5\">EPH 2:4–2:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet5:7\">1PE 5:7</a></p>\n<h3>He defends and protects</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps125:2\">PSA 125:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Chr32:8\">2CH 32:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps41:2\">PSA 41:2</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps57:1\">PSA 57:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa25:4\">ISA 25:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt23:37\">MAT 23:37</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:11\">JHN 17:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess3:3\">2TH 3:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:5\">1PE 1:5</a></p>\n<h3>He teaches and guides</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps25:9\">PSA 25:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut1:33\">DEU 1:33</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:2\">DEU 8:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps139:10\">PSA 139:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov3:5-Prov3:6\">PRO 3:5–3:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa30:21\">ISA 30:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa42:16\">ISA 42:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John16:13\">JHN 16:13</a></p>\n<h3>He keeps and provides</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps23:1\">PSA 23:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen28:15\">GEN 28:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut8:18\">DEU 8:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps121:4\">PSA 121:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mal3:10\">MAL 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim6:17\">1TI 6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim1:12\">2TI 1:12</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jude1:24\">JUD 1:24</a></p>\n<h2>God's guardianship of other things</h2>\n<h3>He is guardian of his word</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:35\">MAT 24:35</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut29:29\">DEU 29:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:18\">MAT 5:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark13:32\">MRK 13:32</a></p>\n<h3>He is guardian of the world</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps24:1\">PSA 24:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:6-Ps33:7\">PSA 33:6–33:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps50:10\">PSA 50:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps89:9\">PSA 89:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps93:1\">PSA 93:1</a></p>\n<h2>Christians are guardians of God's truth</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Thess2:15\">2TH 2:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut6:6-Deut6:7\">DEU 6:6–6:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:11\">GAL 2:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:1\">EPH 4:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:3\">EPH 4:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:27\">PHP 1:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess2:12\">1TH 2:12</a></p>\n<h2>Angelic guardianship</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps91:11-Ps91:12\">PSA 91:11–91:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen3:24\">GEN 3:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod14:19\">EXO 14:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg2:1\">JDG 2:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs6:17\">2KI 6:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps34:7\">PSA 34:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa63:9\">ISA 63:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts8:26\">ACT 8:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts12:15\">ACT 12:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts27:23\">ACT 27:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:19\">GAL 3:19</a></p>",
